MIT License

McAFuse - A FUSE utility to handle McAfee FDE in a digital investigation.

This program expose a static file system containing 2 files:
    - SafeBoot.disk: a fat partition inside the encrypted disk
    - encdisk.img: an image of the encrypted disk to analyze

